(   - mu-plugin) Tj T*
(   - Code Snippets) Tj T*
(   - plugin repo) Tj T*
(   - local package) Tj T*
(2. Back up existing file or record Git status.) Tj T*
(3. Apply smallest patch.) Tj T*
(4. Run syntax/test check.) Tj T*
(5. Verify in browser or HTTP.) Tj T*
(6. Save final explanation.) Tj T*
() Tj T*
(### 4. Review-Only Mode) Tj T*
ET
