(```) Tj T*
() Tj T*
(## Real Failure Lessons To Encode) Tj T*
() Tj T*
(### Case 1: Safety Wording Misrouted To WP Reset) Tj T*
() Tj T*
(Observed failure:) Tj T*
() Tj T*
(- User said "do not publish/delete/reset".) Tj T*
(- Local planner saw `reset` and routed to WP Reset.) Tj T*
() Tj T*
(Fix already started:) Tj T*
() Tj T*
(- `isResetOnlySafetyBoundary\(\)` added in `tools/sidebar-bridge-node/src/local-planner.mjs`.) Tj T*
(- Unit test added in `tools/sidebar-bridge-node/test/local-planner.test.mjs`.) Tj T*
() Tj T*
(Permanent rule:) Tj T*
() Tj T*
(- Negative safety phrases must not become action intent.) Tj T*
(- "do not reset" means block/reset avoidance, not reset execution.) Tj T*
() Tj T*
(Acceptance test:) Tj T*
() Tj T*
(```text) Tj T*
(Goal: "Investigate this WordPress issue. Do not publish/delete/reset anything.") Tj T*
(Expected: no WP Reset route.) Tj T*
(```) Tj T*
() Tj T*
(### Case 2: WordPress Hidden Login Route) Tj T*
() Tj T*
(Observed issue:) Tj T*
() Tj T*
(- Direct `/wp-login.php` failed on one site.) Tj T*
(- Valid login started at `/dashboard`, which redirected to a special login URL.) Tj T*
() Tj T*
(Permanent rule:) Tj T*
() Tj T*
(- If the user provides an admin/dashboard URL, prefer that route over guessing `/wp-login.php`.) Tj T*
(- If direct login fails, inspect redirects before declaring login impossible.) Tj T*
() Tj T*
(Acceptance test:) Tj T*
() Tj T*
(```text) Tj T*
(Input URL: https://example.com/dashboard) Tj T*
(Expected: preserve user-provided login route and follow redirects.) Tj T*
(```) Tj T*
() Tj T*
(### Case 3: Directorist Geo Search No Results) Tj T*
() Tj T*
(Observed issue:) Tj T*
() Tj T*
(- Geolocation filled the visible address.) Tj T*
ET
endstream
