(- Page had multiple Directorist search forms with duplicate `cityLat/cityLng`.) Tj T*
(- Only the first coordinate pair was updated.) Tj T*
(- Submitted form could send address with blank coordinates.) Tj T*
() Tj T*
(Correct workflow:) Tj T*
() Tj T*
(1. Inspect live form fields.) Tj T*
(2. Inspect Directorist query condition.) Tj T*
(3. Verify published listings with known coordinates.) Tj T*
(4. Patch child theme, not core plugin.) Tj T*
(5. Remove old orphan geolocation code.) Tj T*
(6. Verify logged-out page and search results.) Tj T*
() Tj T*
(Permanent rule:) Tj T*
() Tj T*
(- For search bugs, inspect actual request fields before touching code.) Tj T*
(- For repeated forms, check duplicate IDs and submitted form scope.) Tj T*
() Tj T*
(Acceptance test:) Tj T*
() Tj T*
(```text) Tj T*
(Given multiple search forms) Tj T*
(When one form has address text and another has known cityLat/cityLng) Tj T*
(Then the submitted form gets cityLat/cityLng before submit.) Tj T*
(```) Tj T*
() Tj T*
(### Case 4: Draft Test Listing Misleading Search Result) Tj T*
() Tj T*
(Observed issue:) Tj T*
() Tj T*
(- User supplied a preview URL for listing `3862`.) Tj T*
(- The listing was draft.) Tj T*
(- Public search should not return draft content.) Tj T*
() Tj T*
(Permanent rule:) Tj T*
() Tj T*
(- Before using a test listing for public search verification, check status.) Tj T*
(- If it is draft/private/pending, verify against a published listing too.) Tj T*
() Tj T*
(### Case 5: Booking Dropdown Regression) Tj T*
() Tj T*
(Observed issue family:) Tj T*
() Tj T*
(- A previous fix was made for one broken booking condition.) Tj T*
(- A later change risked disrupting original booking dropdown behavior.) Tj T*
() Tj T*
(Permanent rule:) Tj T*
() Tj T*
(- Before editing booking code, inspect the old fix, plugin state, and a comparable working) Tj T*
(local flow.) Tj T*
(- Preserve original plugin behavior unless the defect is proven.) Tj T*
() Tj T*
ET
endstream
