(## Phase 5: Patch Workflow) Tj T*
() Tj T*
(Goal:) Tj T*
() Tj T*
(Make live changes reviewable and rollback-safe.) Tj T*
() Tj T*
(Workflow:) Tj T*
() Tj T*
(1. Read current file.) Tj T*
(2. Save local backup.) Tj T*
(3. Create patched local copy.) Tj T*
(4. Run syntax check.) Tj T*
(5. Submit through correct channel.) Tj T*
(6. Re-read live file.) Tj T*
(7. Verify public page.) Tj T*
() Tj T*
(Required metadata:) Tj T*
() Tj T*
(```json) Tj T*
({) Tj T*
(  "target": "yourspace.global dRestaurant Child functions.php",) Tj T*
(  "backup": "C:/Users/Arafat/Documents/support/...",) Tj T*
(  "patched_copy": "C:/Users/Arafat/Documents/support/...",) Tj T*
(  "syntax_check": "php -l passed",) Tj T*
(  "live_verify": "public page contains new script") Tj T*
(}) Tj T*
(```) Tj T*
() Tj T*
(Acceptance:) Tj T*
() Tj T*
